name: Hammond Manufacturing Company Limited Class A Subordinate Voting Shares
longDescription: Hammond Manufacturing Co Ltd provides electrical and electronic components to Original Equipment Manufacturers (OEM) through a network of agents and distributors. Its product categories include Electrical Enclosures, Small Enclosures, Rack Mounting Solutions, PDUs & Outlet Strips, Transformers, and Classic Transformers & Chokes. Its geographical segments are Canada, the United States, and other countries, of which key revenue is derived from the United States.
